Achievements.Name: Bought a Slot
Achievements.Description: Buy one Plasmid or Tonic Slot at a Gatherer's Garden.

Achievements.Name: Max Plasmid Slots
Achievements.Description: Fully upgrade to the maximum number of Plasmid Slots.

Achievements.Name: Upgraded a Weapon
Achievements.Description: Upgrade any weapon at a Power to the People Station.

Achievements.Name: Fully Upgraded a Weapon
Achievements.Description: Install the third and final upgrade to any of your weapons.

Achievements.Name: All Weapon Upgrades
Achievements.Description: Find all 14 Power to the People weapon upgrades in the game.

Achievements.Name: Prolific Hacker
Achievements.Description: Successfully hack at least one of every type of machine.

Achievements.Name: Master Hacker
Achievements.Description: Hack 30 machines at a distance with the Hack Tool.

Achievements.Name: First Research
Achievements.Description: Research a Splicer with the Research Camera.

Achievements.Name: One Research Track
Achievements.Description: Max out one Research Track.

Achievements.Name: Research Master
Achievements.Description: Max out research on all 9 research subjects.

Achievements.Name: Grand Daddy
Achievements.Description: Defeat 3 Big Daddies without dying during the fight.

Achievements.Name: Master Gatherer
Achievements.Description: Gather 600 ADAM with Little Sisters.

Achievements.Name: Fully Upgraded a Plasmid
Achievements.Description: Fully upgrade one of your Plasmids to the level 3 version at a Gatherer's Garden.

Achievements.Name: All Plasmids
Achievements.Description: Find or purchase all 11 basic Plasmid types.

Achievements.Name: Trap Master
Achievements.Description: Kill 30 enemies using only Traps.

Achievements.Name: Master Protector
Achievements.Description: Get through a Gather with no damage and no one getting to the Little Sister.

Achievements.Name: Big Spender
Achievements.Description: Spend 2000 dollars at Vending Machines.

Achievements.Name: Dealt with Every Little Sister
Achievements.Description: Either Harvest or Save every Little Sister in the game.

Achievements.Name: Against All Odds
Achievements.Description: Finish the game on the hardest difficulty level.

Achievements.Name: Big Brass Balls
Achievements.Description: Finish the game without using Vita-Chambers.

Achievements.Name: Rapture Historian
Achievements.Description: Find 100 audio diaries.

Achievements.Name: Unnatural Selection
Achievements.Description: Score your first kill in a non-private match.

Achievements.Name: Welcome to Rapture
Achievements.Description: Complete your first non-private match.

Achievements.Name: Disgusting Frankenstein
Achievements.Description: Become a Big Daddy for the first time in a non-private match.

Achievements.Name: "Mr. Bubbles-- No!"
Achievements.Description: Take down your first Big Daddy in a non-private match.

Achievements.Name: Mother Goose
Achievements.Description: Save your first Little Sister in a non-private match.

Achievements.Name: Two-Bit Heroics
Achievements.Description: Complete your first trial in a non-private match.

Achievements.Name: Parasite
Achievements.Description: Achieve Rank 10.

Achievements.Name: Little Moth
Achievements.Description: Achieve Rank 20.

Achievements.Name: Skin Job
Achievements.Description: Achieve Rank 30.

Achievements.Name: Choose the Impossible
Achievements.Description: Achieve Rank 40.

Achievements.Name: Proving Grounds
Achievements.Description: Win your first non-private match.

Achievements.Name: Man About Town
Achievements.Description: Play at least one non-private match on each multiplayer map.

Achievements.Name: Daddy's Home
Achievements.Description: Found your way back into the ruins of Rapture.

Achievements.Name: Protector
Achievements.Description: Defended yourself against Lamb's assault in the train station.

Achievements.Name: Sinclairs Solution
Achievements.Description: Joined forces with Sinclair in Ryan Amusements.

Achievements.Name: Confronted Grace
Achievements.Description: Confronted Lambs lieutenant in Paupers Drop.

Achievements.Name: Defeated the Preacher
Achievements.Description: Defeated the Preacher.

Achievements.Name: Nose for News
Achievements.Description: Uncovered the secret of Dionysus Park.

Achievements.Name: Found Lamb's Hideout
Achievements.Description: Gained access to Lambs stronghold.

Achievements.Name: Reunion
Achievements.Description: Reunited with your original Little Sister.

Achievements.Name: Heading to the Surface
Achievements.Description: Headed to the surface on the side of Sinclair's escape pod.

Achievements.Name: Escape
Achievements.Description: Escaped Rapture.

Achievements.Name: 9-Irony
Achievements.Description: Paid your respects to the founder of Rapture.

Achievements.Name: Distance Hacker
Achievements.Description: Used the Hack Tool to hack an object at a distance.

Achievements.Name: Unbreakable
Achievements.Description: Defended yourself against the Big Sister without dying.

Achievements.Name: Look at You, Hacker
Achievements.Description: Killed 50 enemies using only hacked Security.

Achievements.Name: Adopted a Little Sister
Achievements.Description: Adopted a new Little Sister for the first time.

Achievements.Name: Savior
Achievements.Description: Saved every Little Sister and spared Grace, Stanley and Gil.

Achievements.Name: Counterattack
Achievements.Description: Killed an enemy with its own projectile.
